{
  "stem": "9215.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I suppose they came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't-- there was so good made, and painted, and everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They couldn't see this, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we been there for nine days-- no food, no nothing, and-- and-- and nothing to drink.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then my little brother, the youngest, he was, at that time, about 15 or 16 year old.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, I'm going in the next door.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe there's some water or something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he went to the next neighbor, and the neighbor what-- he got arthritis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't laugh, it's true.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he made every night-- he made a bath.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he took a pail of water from the-- from the-- from the-- bath and came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We drink that water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know something?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We took a pail, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we did everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Nine days we been there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then one night-- What-- what did you-- what did you do for food?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You found some food?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got the water.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Do not ask me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one night, we hear it's thundering-- terrible!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But wait-- where we was hiding-- by every house was a German and a Ukrainian across, you know?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They know-- they knew that there is people what hiding in the houses.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They waiting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said maybe somebody will run out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They'll shoot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But my brother said-- the older brother said, this night, they wouldn't be here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's terrible.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's raining.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It thundering.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this-- this night, we escaped from the hiding, from the wall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- they started shoot through the walls a week-- nine days-- a week after the-- the end of the Jewish holidays-- 1942.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first one was my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- she didn't-- she said, I'll go the first.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you hear shooting, she said, do not-- don't go.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
